# Prompt 2 (optional)
# Type "<follow-up prompt>"
# Sleep 2s
# Enter
#
# If needed, reuse the long nudge block above.

# Prompt 3 (optional)
# Type "<second follow-up prompt>"
# Sleep 2s
# Enter
#
# If needed, reuse the long nudge block above.

# Nudge TUI to scroll to input area
Type " "
Backspace
Sleep 3s

# Exit cleanly
Ctrl+C
Sleep 1s
